          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1713277372994-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil half a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and your <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) in 200ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [260ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml]</span><strong> boiled water </strong>– this is your<strong> chipotle stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1713277391727-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1713277391727-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1713277391727-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1713277391727-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1713277391727-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>,<strong> ground smoked paprika</strong> and <strong>ground</strong> <strong>cumin</strong> to the pot and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Drain and rinse your<strong> black beans</strong></p><p>Once fragrant, add the<strong> drained black beans</strong> and<strong> chipotle stock</strong> and cook, covered for 5-7 min or until the beans are soft enough to mash</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1713277404909-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1713277404909-x400.jpg",
