          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1713277425530-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Chop your <strong>hake</strong> into large, bite-sized pieces and season with a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped hake</strong> to the pan and cook for 3-4 min on each side, or until cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1713277439043-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1713277439043-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1713277439043-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1713277439043-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1713277439043-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the hake is cooked, add it to a bowl with your <strong>mango chutney</strong>, <strong>sliced spring onion </strong>and <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Zest and juice <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s]</strong> into the bowl and give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> zesty lime hake</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1713277448915-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1713277448915-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1713277448915-x700.jpg",
